data.description: NESTLED AMONG THE SPRAWLING FARMLAND JUST MINUTES FROM TOWN! This custom home is in the country; however, it is just a short drive to the city, and it is close to schools. Easy living is enjoyed in this open floor plan with 3 bedrooms plus bonus room. In addition to the formal dining, the kitchen has large breakfast room and huge walk-in pantry. The owner's suite has tray ceiling, large closet, and lovely bathroom with large garden tub and shower. The remaining two bedrooms have a Jack and Jill bathroom and not only this bath, but also the owner's suite, both bathrooms have blue tooth enabled bathroom exhaust fans. This home also has a screened porch and patio. This home is on 3 acres! The seller is willing pay $3000 of the buyers closing cost with a full price offer.
